 The Tramways building in the Baakens Valley was awash with colour and style on Monday night at the Jenni Gault Bella Babe 2017 gala. Bay designer Yvette Peo presented her Elegant Ivy range of evening wear, modelled by the 13 Bella Babe finalists. Ilisma Janse van Rensburg took home the title, with style and glamour were the winner on the night.
